**Missing libs:** `nix-locate -w libfoo.so`. Common: numpy/scipy ‚Üí blas/lapack; cryptography ‚Üí openssl, libffi; lxml ‚Üí libxml2; pillow ‚Üí libjpeg, zlib; psycopg2 ‚Üí postgresql. Darwin adds Security framework.

**Anti-patterns:** No `import <nixpkgs>`. No `python3.withPackages` ‚Äî use `uv add`. No `uv venv` on every `nix develop` ‚Äî check `if [ ! -d .venv ]` first. Use `packages = [...]` not `buildInputs` for devShell.

**Verification:** `nix flake check` | `nix develop` | `python --version` | `uv --version` | `python -c "import requests"`

**Lookup:** Use nixos-mcp for `python313`, `uv`, and system packages.
